                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On October 24, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_NSM1">Sardar Mohammed
                        Naim</persName> discussed with <persName corresp="#p_BDKE1">Bruce</persName>
                    the Pushtunistan question and other issues in the light of the recent Soviet <hi
                        rend="italic">démarche</hi>. The memorandum of this conversation is printed
                    on <ref target="#pg_1376">page 1376</ref>.</p>
                <p>On October 29, a conversation on similar subjects took place in New York between
                    the Secretary, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_NSM1">Naim</persName>, and
                        <persName corresp="#p_LL1">Mohammed Kabir Ludin</persName>, Afghan
                    Representative at the United Nations. For the memorandum of this conversation,
                    see <ref target="#pg_1378">page 1378</ref>.</p>
            </div>
